{"word":"στέρομαι","slug":"στέρομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στέρομαι</b></el> <el>(στέρομαι,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>only in <a href='S:present tense'>pres.</a> and <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <el>στερέομαι</el>\n<p/><i>to be wanting in, to lack, want</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>carere</el>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic:—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to suffer loss</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}